  She needed to cover up in the warm coat thanks to New York City's 50F-degree winter weather. Ana wore her glossy, brunette locks in a natural down hairstyle and opted for a glossy, sophisticated makeup look with some dark eyeliner. She accessorised with some pointed, silver stilettos and dark nail polish on her toes and fingernails. That same day, the Hollywood Foreign Press Association announced that the Knives Out actress would be presenting during the 80th annual Golden Globes, which air next Tuesday on NBC.   